{"tid":545480,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[南法] 行程問題求助","createTime":"2018-01-30T14:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T18:54:10.000Z","uid":40542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"377a122e16dd90b856879aa4938d57869af29cc9","tid":545480,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"小弟下個月去7日南法，尼斯落機，<br />\n暫定一日一個town咁玩，住尼斯三日，住Avignon三日，無車，<br />\n但決定唔到去邊個好，想問問巴打意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>蔚藍海岸</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">尼斯</span><br />\n[五揀二]<br />\nEze<br />\nMonaco<br />\nAntibes<br />\nMenton<br />\nCannes<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>普羅旺斯</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">Avignon</span><br />\n[五揀二]<br />\nSt. Remy<br />\nArles<br />\nNimes<br />\n索格島 + 碧泉村<br />\nLourmarin<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e574e8e5fd064b9cbe417e6d40633e0115f65d","tid":545480,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410d3c50ee43d875b3736bf3638484f5351b5f41","tid":545480,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05f6aa434279f661f5952b214d347eef50300fcc","tid":545480,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T21:13:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca3812729def8cbad733ee239265e9dcd0a72bb9","tid":545480,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5aa8138ab87e7af5c767d2fe289fae88fd28d0d1","tid":545480,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2608605540442f221473a483a3c9789ef98dfd14","tid":545480,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:18:08.000Z","msg":"Avignon:<br />\n你search下石頭城同紅土城啦.<br />\n可以一戰!"},{"pid":"09c5a6b885e780d90fdf7bb7484e20e25d8e634d","tid":545480,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"剩係去過Provence既Avignon, Arles 同索格島<br />\nAvignon 好適合做中心點，其他地方一日遊都夠 推介你住Avignon火車站隔離間酒店 好似係ibis, 超級方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdb0b7cd2d9c0bcde4bbee3635a670d75f56eec","tid":545480,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T20:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人去過馬賽"},{"pid":"226500f39db1c3f92719f8f520a8ad8d1d9dd61a","tid":545480,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T22:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人去過馬賽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d35e4e6fc1a7b43e3102e6c4d87f01b27d6166b","tid":545480,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"226500f39db1c3f92719f8f520a8ad8d1d9dd61a","tid":545480,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T22:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人去過馬賽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"如何"},{"pid":"ba3619d4a5fac565a39380